<p>Always well dressed, Eric is very charismatic.He believes it’s important to leave a good impression. After school, he likes to hang out with friends and play videogames or basketball.On the weekends, he likes participating in the church choir. His mother taught him to sing Christian gospel music and now, singing gospel music has become one of his favorite past times. When first meeting Eric you may find him shy, but he’s quick to open up.He’s looking forward to having parents who are strong role models.He wants to be part of a patient family who will be involved in his counseling and who will be happy to share his successes.Eric also wants to be part of a family whowill help him remain in contact with his two brothers.</p>
